## How to run

| OS | What to do |
|---|---|
| **macOS** | Double-click `START_HERE.command`. If Gatekeeper blocks: right-click → Open → Open. |
| **Windows** | Double-click `START_HERE.bat`. If SmartScreen blocks: *More info* → *Run anyway*. |
| **Linux** | Open terminal in this folder and run `./start_here.sh`. |
| **Any OS (power user)** | `Rscript setup_and_run.R --quick --data /path/to/file` |

**Only requirement:** R 4.0+ from https://cran.r-project.org/

